dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Russell Campbell. May I have your name, please?

Sure, my policy number is five six eight two one and my date of birth is zero four dash one zero dash one nine eight seven.
Thank you for the information, Carolyn. Now, could you confirm your current mailing address and phone number?
Of course. My mailing address is one two three Maple Street, Cityville, State, and my phone number is five five five dash three three three dash eight eight eight eight.
Great, thank you for confirming that, Carolyn. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
Not at the moment, thank you.
You're welcome, Carolyn. Thank you for your time today. Have a great day!
